title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - Aircraft  & Avionics Update - Garmin G5000
description:
In this video we will have a look at the Garmin G5000 in the Citation Longitude which received a massive update as part of  1st beta release for the Aircraft & Avionics Update (AAU) 1. We will start with a tour through the cockpit and will continue having a look at the major changes the aviation systems did receive.
